message: Hello! Thank you for contacting Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Hi Chris! I'm a happy customer with a question about my policy.
That's great to hear! I'm here to help. Before proceeding, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Of course, my full name is Sarah Johnson.
Thank you for completing security, Sarah. How can I assist you with your policy today?
I'm looking to make a claim on my policy due to a recent car accident. Can you help me with that?
I'm deeply sorry to hear about your car accident, Sarah. Let me see how we can assist you. Could you please confirm your date of birth?
Thank you for the information, Sarah. I'll run through security one more time. Can you confirm the first line of your address and postcode?
Sure, my address is 123 Green Street, London, L1 2AB.
That's all correct, Sarah. I appreciate your patience. Let's see how we can assist with your claim. A possible resolution could be to start the claims process online. Would that work for you?
Thank you for your help, Chris. Starting the claim online sounds good. I appreciate your assistance.
I'm glad that I was able to help, Sarah. If you need any further assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out. Have a great day!
